'Over course of the game we defended very well and limited them to very few chances, but the mistake we made we got punished for where we were just too deep.

'Obviously I'm proud of the team and the young players who gained experience in a fantastic atmosphere.

'We now just have to concentrate on a league campaign that's starting to go well for us. The object of our season is to win a cup but we've got an excellent opportunity in other competitions.' 

